<text><body>
<lb n="0783b10" ed="T"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="0783b11" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0783b12" ed="T"/><cb:docNumber>No. 513</cb:docNumber>
<lb n="0783b13" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><note n="0783026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔佛說〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0783026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">佛說【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0783026"><lem wit="【大】">佛說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>琉璃王經</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0783b14" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0783b15" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator"><note n="0783027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">西晉月氏國＝晉世【宋】【元】【宮】，晉【明】</note><note n="0783027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">西晉月氏國【大】，晉世【宋】【元】【宮】，晉【明】</note><app n="0783027"><lem wit="【大】">西晉月氏國</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】">晉世</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">晉</rdg></app>三藏竺法護<note n="0783028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（別）＋譯【宋】【元】【宮】</note><note n="0783028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">譯【大】，別譯【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="0783028"><lem wit="【大】">譯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】">別譯</rdg></app></byline>
<lb n="0783b16" ed="T"/><cb:div type="jing"><p xml:id="pT14p0783b1601">聞如是：</p><p xml:id="pT14p0783b1604" rend="inline">一時，佛遊迦維羅衛釋氏精舍，尼
<lb n="0783b17" ed="T"/>拘類樹下，與五百比丘、侍者阿難、金剛力士
<lb n="0783b18" ed="T"/>樓由俱。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0783b1804" rend="inline">於城中有舍夷貴姓五百長者，共為
<lb n="0783b19" ed="T"/>世尊造立講堂，自相<note n="0783029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">興＝與【宮】</note><note n="0783029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">興【大】，與【宮】</note><app n="0783029"><lem wit="【大】">興</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">與</rdg></app>誓：「講堂成已，當請
<lb n="0783b20" ed="T"/>正覺於上設供，沙門、梵志、長者居士、群黎人
<lb n="0783b21" ed="T"/>民，不得先佛妄昇此堂；若違要者，罪在不
<lb n="0783b22" ed="T"/>測。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0783b2202" rend="inline">舍衛國王，時有太子名維樓黎——產育之
<lb n="0783b23" ed="T"/>初，與琉璃寶俱，因以為號——領衛士定省外
<lb n="0783b24" ed="T"/>氏，方來入城，見視講堂，高廣嚴淨，都雅殊
<lb n="0783b25" ed="T"/>妙，世所希有，則於其上，頓止息涼。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0783b2514" rend="inline">監講堂
<lb n="0783b26" ed="T"/>者，往白諸貴姓言：「舍衛太子來止講堂。」貴
<lb n="0783b27" ed="T"/>姓聞之，興怒罵曰：「吾等家產。有何異德，敢
<lb n="0783b28" ed="T"/>登此堂？本造斯殿，乃為佛舉，當具上饌，延
<lb n="0783b29" ed="T"/>屈世尊至真聖眾，供養畢訖，然後吾等乃宜
<pb n="0783c" ed="T" xml:id="T14.0513.0783c"/>
<lb n="0783c01" ed="T"/>自處；而微者前尊，置體于此。」尋遣使者<note n="0783030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">面＝而【三】【宮】</note><note n="0783030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">面【大】，而【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0783030"><lem wit="【大】">面</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">而</rdg></app>
<lb n="0783c02" ed="T"/>罵辱之，催逐發遣，令不久滯，所蹈之地，剗
<lb n="0783c03" ed="T"/>去足跡，所履寶階，輒更貿易。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0783c0312" rend="inline">時，琉璃太子
<lb n="0783c04" ed="T"/>聞其罵音，姿色變動，心懷毒恚，勅太史曰：「深
<lb n="0783c05" ed="T"/>憶記之，<note n="0783031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">須＝頃【宋】【元】</note><note n="0783031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">須【大】，頃【宋】【元】</note><app n="0783031"><lem wit="【大】">須</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">頃</rdg></app>吾為王，當誅此類。」太史阿薩陀
<lb n="0783c06" ed="T"/><note place="inline"><note n="0783032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">晉＝此【明】</note><note n="0783032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">晉【大】，此【明】</note><app n="0783032"><lem wit="【大】">晉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">此</rdg></app>名無信</note>能觀天文、占究災怪，令書此狀內于帶中，
<lb n="0783c07" ed="T"/><note n="0783033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">俠＝挾【元】【明】</note><note n="0783033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">俠【大】，挾【元】【明】</note><app n="0783033"><lem wit="【大】">俠</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">挾</rdg></app>惡識非，嚴退還歸，不復前至朝覲外家。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0783c0717" rend="inline">太
<lb n="0783c08" ed="T"/>子父王名波斯匿，與后末利，駕乘導從，詣
<lb n="0783c09" ed="T"/>祇樹園。下車却蓋，免冠解劍，屏拂脫屣，除
<lb n="0783c10" ed="T"/>四種兵。步涉小徑，與末利俱，五體投地，稽
<lb n="0783c11" ed="T"/>首為禮，却坐一面。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0783c1108" rend="inline">琉璃太子時歸還宮，無
<lb n="0783c12" ed="T"/>所瞻覩，問左右曰：「父王、太后今為<note n="0783034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">所＋（在）【三】</note><note n="0783034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">所【大】，所在【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0783034"><lem wit="【大】">所</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">所在</rdg></app>？」<note n="0783035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">湊＝奏【三】【宮】</note><note n="0783035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">湊【大】，奏【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0783035"><lem wit="【大】">湊</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">奏</rdg></app>
<lb n="0783c13" ed="T"/>曰：「造佛。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0783c1304" rend="inline">太子聞問，欣率所領，不復解嚴，遂
<lb n="0783c14" ed="T"/>至精舍，曰：「宜知是時。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0783c1409" rend="inline">於是，太子逼害翼從、
<lb n="0783c15" ed="T"/>王之近臣，五百餘人，一時夷滅，却王冠幘蓋
<lb n="0783c16" ed="T"/>劍拂履服乘諸飾，外無白者。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0783c1612" rend="inline">於時，世尊為
<lb n="0783c17" ed="T"/>王及后說世無常、愛欲合、會別離法句，王立
<lb n="0783c18" ed="T"/>不退轉，后得覩道迹。佛說經已，王稽首退，
<lb n="0783c19" ed="T"/>不見侍輔，而僵尸狼籍，<note n="0783036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">唯＝惟【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0783036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">唯【大】＊，惟【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0783036"><lem wit="【大】">唯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">惟</rdg></app>王衣冠二人得
<lb n="0783c20" ed="T"/>免，逃入樹間，還與王遇。王問之曰：「群僚所
<lb n="0783c21" ed="T"/>在？」二人答曰：「太子率勒所統，<note n="0783037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">脇＝愶【三】【宮】</note><note n="0783037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">脇【大】，愶【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0783037"><lem wit="【大】">脇</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">愶</rdg></app>將還宮。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0783c2116" rend="inline">王
<lb n="0783c22" ed="T"/>謂末利：「子造不順，謀逆如斯。素知此，吾當避，
<lb n="0783c23" ed="T"/>以國付，之精舍。」左<note n="0783038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">有＝右【三】【宮】</note><note n="0783038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">有【大】，右【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0783038"><lem wit="【大】">有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">右</rdg></app>族姓，愍王及后體柔
<lb n="0783c24" ed="T"/>狀樂不堪<note n="0783039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">步＋（涉）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0783039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">步【大】，步涉【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0783039"><lem wit="【大】">步</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">步涉</rdg></app>，濟以車乘，弊陋難處，遂昇進邁
<lb n="0783c25" ed="T"/>至于城門。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0783c2505" rend="inline">先時，太子列五百人置門鎮衛，勅
<lb n="0783c26" ed="T"/>門監曰：「若父王來，勿聽使入。」王曰：「若不得
<lb n="0783c27" ed="T"/>入，吾將焉如？」曰：「詔大王當令出境。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0783c2714" rend="inline">時，王波斯
<lb n="0783c28" ed="T"/>匿涕泣哽<note n="0783040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">噎＝咽【三】【宮】</note><note n="0783040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">噎【大】，咽【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0783040"><lem wit="【大】">噎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">咽</rdg></app>，以偈歎曰：</p>
<lb n="0783c29" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT14p0783c2901" rend="margin-left:1em;text-indent:-1em"><l>「誠哉世尊教，</l><l>所演審而諦，</l>
<pb n="0784a" ed="T" xml:id="T14.0513.0784a"/>
<lb n="0784a01" ed="T"/><l>興衰與貴賤，</l><l>一切無常住。</l>
<lb n="0784a02" ed="T"/><l>寧守戒念道，</l><l>不貪厚俸祿，</l>
<lb n="0784a03" ed="T"/><l>僥聞講法會，</l><l>不願億國土。</l>
<lb n="0784a04" ed="T"/><l>王據國恣情，</l><l>饕穢遑所<note n="0784a0401" resp="CBETA" type="add">欲【CB】【麗-CB】，樂【大】</note><app n="0784a0401"><lem resp="CBETA.maha CBETA.say" wit="【CB】【麗-CB】">欲<note type="cf1">K19n0787_p0891c11</note></lem><rdg wit="【大】">樂</rdg></app>，</l>
<lb n="0784a05" ed="T"/><l>聞法蒙解脫，</l><l>塵垢用<note n="0784001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">消＝銷【宮】</note><note n="0784001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">消【大】，銷【宮】</note><app n="0784001"><lem wit="【大】">消</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">銷</rdg></app>除。」</l></lg>
<lb n="0784a06" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT14p0784a0601">爾時，觀者無數千人，聞王歎音，八百人發
<lb n="0784a07" ed="T"/>大道意，皆立不退，<note n="0784002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔轉〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0784002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">轉【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0784002"><lem wit="【大】">轉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>憂色不悅。王后末利
<lb n="0784a08" ed="T"/>白王曰：「幸勿愁憒，可共俱逝還我父國。」即
<lb n="0784a09" ed="T"/>便進發，七日七夜，到迦維羅衛兜薩聚，值
<lb n="0784a10" ed="T"/>冥門閉，亦不得入。各共<note n="0784003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">飢＝饑【明】</note><note n="0784003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">飢【大】，饑【明】</note><app n="0784003"><lem wit="【大】">飢</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">饑</rdg></app>渴，無所向仰，求
<lb n="0784a11" ed="T"/>乞無地，止於水傍人洗菜處，得迸<note n="0784004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蘿＝羅【三】【宮】</note><note n="0784004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">蘿【大】，羅【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0784004"><lem wit="【大】">蘿</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">羅</rdg></app>蔔食
<lb n="0784a12" ed="T"/>之，臚脹<note n="0784005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">腹＝膓【宮】</note><note n="0784005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">腹【大】，膓【宮】</note><app n="0784005"><lem wit="【大】">腹</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">膓</rdg></app>痛而薨。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0784a1208" rend="inline">王后悲<note n="0784006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">慟＝動【元】【明】</note><note n="0784006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">慟【大】，動【元】【明】</note><app n="0784006"><lem wit="【大】">慟</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">動</rdg></app>，舉聲大哭，
<lb n="0784a13" ed="T"/>守聚者問曰：「何人乎？」曰：「吾王后也。」又問：「王
<lb n="0784a14" ed="T"/>為在何乎？」后曰：「痛哉！王薨水側。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0784a1413" rend="inline">聚守門者
<lb n="0784a15" ed="T"/>即馳白舍夷諸貴姓，<note n="0784007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">貴＝憒【宮】</note><note n="0784007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">貴【大】，憒【宮】</note><app n="0784007"><lem wit="【大】">貴</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">憒</rdg></app>姓聞凶，奔波驚愕，
<lb n="0784a16" ed="T"/>尋皆來，出<note n="0784008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">賵＝胃【宮】</note><note n="0784008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">賵【大】，胃【宮】</note><app n="0784008"><lem wit="【大】">賵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">胃</rdg></app>贈殯棺，闍維如法，咸皆號悼，
<lb n="0784a17" ed="T"/>莫不摧感。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0784a1705" rend="inline">爾時，貴族釋摩男者，瞿夷之父也，
<lb n="0784a18" ed="T"/>與諸豪右，以偈歎曰：</p>
<lb n="0784a19" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT14p0784a1901" rend="margin-left:1em;text-indent:-1em"><l>「有子有財思惟波波，</l><l>我自非我何有子財，</l>
<lb n="0784a20" ed="T"/><l>愚癡自怙豪尊有終，</l><l>太子用國殪入地獄。」</l></lg>
<lb n="0784a21" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT14p0784a2101">釋氏貴姓二百五十，深惟無常，得不退轉。五
<lb n="0784a22" ed="T"/>百女人，未出家者，得不起法忍。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0784a2213" rend="inline">於是，琉璃
<lb n="0784a23" ed="T"/>太子聞父王薨，即在殿稱制為王。異道太史
<lb n="0784a24" ed="T"/>出帶中書，證案本狀記惡之<note n="0784009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">忌＝忘【元】【明】</note><note n="0784009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">忌【大】，忘【元】【明】</note><app n="0784009"><lem wit="【大】">忌</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">忘</rdg></app>。聞之大怒，
<lb n="0784a25" ed="T"/>心意憤踊，召四種兵，伐迦維羅衛。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0784a2514" rend="inline">佛知其
<lb n="0784a26" ed="T"/>意，從精舍出，止于路要，坐於<note n="0784010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">荄＝萎【元】【明】</note><note n="0784010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">荄【大】，萎【元】【明】</note><app n="0784010"><lem wit="【大】">荄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">萎</rdg></app>枯樹下。斯
<lb n="0784a27" ed="T"/>須之頃，太子軍至。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0784a2708" rend="inline">時，琉璃王遙見世尊，即
<lb n="0784a28" ed="T"/>便下象車，稽首于地，長跪問佛：「唯，天中天！
<lb n="0784a29" ed="T"/>有菩提附差、尼拘類、<note n="0784011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">畢＝祕【三】【宮】</note><note n="0784011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">畢【大】，祕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0784011"><lem wit="【大】">畢</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">祕</rdg></app>鉢、優<note n="0784012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">曇＝蠱【三】【宮】</note><note n="0784012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">曇【大】，蠱【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0784012"><lem wit="【大】">曇</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">蠱</rdg></app>鉢、薩羅、
<pb n="0784b" ed="T" xml:id="T14.0513.0784b"/>
<lb n="0784b01" ed="T"/>怛羅、揵尼赦羅，有此七樹，其蔭高大，有德
<lb n="0784b02" ed="T"/>茂盛，何因棄捨，處枯槁多刺樹耶？」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0784b0214" rend="inline">佛告琉璃
<lb n="0784b03" ed="T"/>王：「雖有七樹，樹蔭茂盛，盛豈有常？吾坐刺樹，
<lb n="0784b04" ed="T"/>以為安隱，用哀愍傷親屬故也。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0784b0413" rend="inline">王心念言：「先
<lb n="0784b05" ed="T"/>古所載，藏室祕讖，用兵征旅遇沙門者，轉
<lb n="0784b06" ed="T"/>迴軍還，況今值佛，焉得進乎？」稽首佛足，即
<lb n="0784b07" ed="T"/>便反旅。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0784b0704" rend="inline">還于舍衛來日未久，侍者阿難、力
<lb n="0784b08" ed="T"/>士樓由，翼從世尊還尼拘類園，令阿難敷
<lb n="0784b09" ed="T"/>座，宣告四輩，皆令集會。時佛尊顏姿容無
<lb n="0784b10" ed="T"/>燿，項無光明，衣服變色。阿難察坐<note n="0784013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">已＝以【三】【宮】</note><note n="0784013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">已【大】，以【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0784013"><lem wit="【大】">已</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">以</rdg></app>定，則
<lb n="0784b11" ed="T"/>整衣法服，右膝投地，叉手白言：「侍尊積年，
<lb n="0784b12" ed="T"/>未覩三變。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0784b1205" rend="inline">佛告阿難：「却<note n="0784014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">數＝後【三】＊</note><note n="0784014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">數【大】＊，後【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0784014"><lem wit="【大】">數</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">後</rdg></app>七日，迦維羅衛
<lb n="0784b13" ed="T"/>釋氏貴姓，皆當傷斃。現斯變者，為<note n="0784015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">中家＝家中【三】【宮】</note><note n="0784015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">中家【大】，家中【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0784015"><lem wit="【大】">中家</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">家中</rdg></app>持
<lb n="0784b14" ed="T"/>服故也。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0784b1404" rend="inline">大目揵連前白世尊：「是何足言？我
<lb n="0784b15" ed="T"/>之神力，正覺所究，能以右掌，舉舍夷國，跳
<lb n="0784b16" ed="T"/>置空中，上不至天，下不至地，琉璃王殺焉
<lb n="0784b17" ed="T"/>能得乎？」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0784b1704" rend="inline">佛告目連：「知汝威德，<note n="0784016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">過＝通【元】【明】</note><note n="0784016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">過【大】，通【元】【明】</note><app n="0784016"><lem wit="【大】">過</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">通</rdg></app>足如斯，
<lb n="0784b18" ed="T"/>宿命之罪，誰當代受？」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0784b1809" rend="inline">又曰：「能以鐵文籠，䟽
<lb n="0784b19" ed="T"/>遮此國，上又以<note n="0784017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鉢＝盋【宋】【元】【宮】</note><note n="0784017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">鉢【大】，盋【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="0784017"><lem wit="【大】">鉢</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】">盋</rdg></app>覆，使無形候，擲置他方
<lb n="0784b20" ed="T"/>異土；又以四披須彌山，南內著于山，然後
<lb n="0784b21" ed="T"/>合之，各得所安；又大海水，深廣之量，三百
<lb n="0784b22" ed="T"/>三十六萬里，我以此國，浮置中央，令諸人
<lb n="0784b23" ed="T"/>民無往來想；又<note n="0784018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔一〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0784018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">一【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0784018"><lem wit="【大】">一</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>以此國，倚須彌山頂，復
<lb n="0784b24" ed="T"/>能倒覆，令無毀害；又下沒之金剛地際，又
<lb n="0784b25" ed="T"/>打擲于琉璃王眾四種之兵，置大鐵圍山表，
<lb n="0784b26" ed="T"/>使兩怨敵不相討伐。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0784b2609" rend="inline">佛言：「善哉！世尊信汝，此
<lb n="0784b27" ed="T"/>十威力，能辦此舉。舍夷貴戚，宿世殃罪，孰
<lb n="0784b28" ed="T"/>堪畢償而代受者？」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0784b2808" rend="inline">阿難白佛：「寧有譎詭，祐護
<lb n="0784b29" ed="T"/>此國，令安隱乎？」佛言：「若舍夷人能同心，不
<pb n="0784c" ed="T" xml:id="T14.0513.0784c"/>
<lb n="0784c01" ed="T"/>與外讎有往來緣，國可全也。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0784c0112" rend="inline">太史三諫：「王
<lb n="0784c02" ed="T"/>宜用時進討舍夷。」王聞赫怒，興軍勒眾。世
<lb n="0784c03" ed="T"/>尊知之，還坐枯樹。如是至三，王亦三還。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0784c0316" rend="inline">第
<lb n="0784c04" ed="T"/>四征時，佛不遂屬，精銳四品之兵，到舍夷
<lb n="0784c05" ed="T"/>國界。釋氏豪姓，<note n="0784019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">又＝右【三】【宮】</note><note n="0784019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">又【大】，右【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0784019"><lem wit="【大】">又</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">右</rdg></app>亦多集，眾出而禦之。族
<lb n="0784c06" ed="T"/>黨<note n="0784020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">驍＝膠【宮】</note><note n="0784020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">驍【大】，膠【宮】</note><app n="0784020"><lem wit="【大】">驍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">膠</rdg></app>勇，強盛善射，射四十里者、射二十里
<lb n="0784c07" ed="T"/>者、十里者、七里者<note n="0784021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">任＝在【明】</note><note n="0784021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">任【大】，在【明】</note><app n="0784021"><lem wit="【大】">任</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">在</rdg></app>其本德，御飛破<note n="0784022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">初＝的【明】</note><note n="0784022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">初【大】，的【明】</note><app n="0784022"><lem wit="【大】">初</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">的</rdg></app>，
<lb n="0784c08" ed="T"/>箭不虛發，能<note n="0784023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">析＝折【三】【宮】</note><note n="0784023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">析【大】，折【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0784023"><lem wit="【大】">析</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">折</rdg></app>一髮，以為七分，去有里數
<lb n="0784c09" ed="T"/>射盡中之，尋聲應弦，曾無遺漏。於是交戰，
<lb n="0784c10" ed="T"/>射琉璃王軍，穿幡折幢，裂蓋摧杠；截轅<note n="0784024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">𩌹＝韅【三】【宮】</note><note n="0784024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">𩌹【大】，韅【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0784024"><lem wit="【大】">𩌹</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">韅</rdg></app>
<lb n="0784c11" ed="T"/><note n="0784025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">攝＝弽【元】【明】</note><note n="0784025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">攝【大】，弽【元】【明】</note><app n="0784025"><lem wit="【大】">攝</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">弽</rdg></app>，決鎧帶<note n="0784026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">韅＝<g ref="#CB10392"/>【元】【明】</note><note n="0784026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">韅【大】，<g ref="#CB10392"/>【元】【明】</note><app n="0784026"><lem wit="【大】">韅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】"><g ref="#CB10392"/></rdg></app>；絕弓弩弦，不害象馬牛畜
<lb n="0784c12" ed="T"/>之命；射<note n="0784027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">珥＝耳【宮】</note><note n="0784027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">珥【大】，耳【宮】</note><app n="0784027"><lem wit="【大】">珥</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">耳</rdg></app>臂指環釧瓔珞，而不中肌；翦除
<lb n="0784c13" ed="T"/><note n="0784028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鬚＝鬢【三】【宮】</note><note n="0784028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">鬚【大】，鬢【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0784028"><lem wit="【大】">鬚</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">鬢</rdg></app>髮左右眉鬚髮毛睫，亦不害體。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0784c1314" rend="inline">琉璃怖
<lb n="0784c14" ed="T"/>駭，問臣下曰：「敵去此幾何？而箭所至傷毀
<lb n="0784c15" ed="T"/>若茲。」答曰：「或四十里、二十里、十里，近者七
<lb n="0784c16" ed="T"/>里。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0784c1602" rend="inline">王聞加悸，不能自寧，將破敵軍，即悸退
<lb n="0784c17" ed="T"/>還。太史諫曰：「大王莫懼！慎無敗却。舍夷人
<lb n="0784c18" ed="T"/>民，皆奉佛戒，為清信士，慈仁不殺，以箭恐
<lb n="0784c19" ed="T"/>人，無傷害意，寧自喪身，不夭生命。且更整
<lb n="0784c20" ed="T"/>陣，<note n="0784029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">併＝并【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0784029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">併【大】＊，并【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0784029"><lem wit="【大】">併</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">并</rdg></app>心撲討，將牢持重，尅捷不久。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0784c2014" rend="inline">諸臣啟
<lb n="0784c21" ed="T"/>曰：「察敵軍射，陷遠無形，非力所<note n="0784030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">距＝拒【三】【宮】</note><note n="0784030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">距【大】，拒【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0784030"><lem wit="【大】">距</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">拒</rdg></app>，懼被摧
<lb n="0784c22" ed="T"/>折，永令臣等為糜戮之，<note n="0784031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">慮＝虜【三】【宮】</note><note n="0784031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">慮【大】，虜【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0784031"><lem wit="【大】">慮</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">虜</rdg></app>箭不可當，置時
<lb n="0784c23" ed="T"/><note n="0784032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">據安＝安據【三】【宮】</note><note n="0784032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">據安【大】，安據【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0784032"><lem wit="【大】">據安</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">安據</rdg></app>，小史之謀，不足專從，各各心動，志<note n="0784033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">在＝存【三】【宮】</note><note n="0784033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">在【大】，存【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0784033"><lem wit="【大】">在</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">存</rdg></app>
<lb n="0784c24" ed="T"/>迸徂。」王大奮怒，催勅進戰。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0784c2411" rend="inline">舍夷外眾，奔走
<lb n="0784c25" ed="T"/><note n="0784034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">保＝堡【三】【宮】</note><note n="0784034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">保【大】，堡【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0784034"><lem wit="【大】">保</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">堡</rdg></app>城，閉門自固，列陣圍繞。至于七日，示悟
<lb n="0784c26" ed="T"/>去就，招懷誘納，唱令內<note n="0784035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">寇＝冠【三】【宮】</note><note n="0784035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">寇【大】，冠【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0784035"><lem wit="【大】">寇</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">冠</rdg></app>，宜時歸命，若不
<lb n="0784c27" ed="T"/>出降，殄滅爾類。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0784c2707" rend="inline">釋氏共議，當堅城守禦當閉
<lb n="0784c28" ed="T"/>門稽顙，當密潛奔竄，躊躇狼狽，則各賦籌，
<lb n="0784c29" ed="T"/>驗定眾心。受籌者多，不受者少，以少從多，
<pb n="0785a" ed="T" xml:id="T14.0513.0785a"/>
<lb n="0785a01" ed="T"/>開門助惡成禍，內與外應，欲令敵勝。勸善
<lb n="0785a02" ed="T"/>者少，得開門入，<note n="0785001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔入〕－【元】【明】</note><note n="0785001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">入【大】，〔－〕【元】【明】</note><app n="0785001"><lem wit="【大】">入</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app><note n="0785002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">挌＝格【三】【宮】</note><note n="0785002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">挌【大】，格【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0785002"><lem wit="【大】">挌</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">格</rdg></app>殺門衛五百人，斬
<lb n="0785a03" ed="T"/>害不<note n="0785003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">訾＝貲【宮】</note><note n="0785003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">訾【大】，貲【宮】</note><app n="0785003"><lem wit="【大】">訾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">貲</rdg></app>，生縛貴姓三萬人，埋著于地，但令
<lb n="0785a04" ed="T"/>頭現，驅迫群象，比足蹈殺，然後駕犁而耕
<lb n="0785a05" ed="T"/>其首，值此酷者，皆須陀洹。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0785a0511" rend="inline">釋摩男者，波斯
<lb n="0785a06" ed="T"/>匿之舊好也，自謂國人：「諦觀無常，苦毒之
<lb n="0785a07" ed="T"/>對，宿罪當償，勿懷怨恨，生現尋死，存者忽
<lb n="0785a08" ed="T"/>終，若干之痛斧解五<note n="0785004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">杌＝兀【宮】</note><note n="0785004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">杌【大】，兀【宮】</note><app n="0785004"><lem wit="【大】">杌</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">兀</rdg></app>。」喟然悲歎：「食福同
<lb n="0785a09" ed="T"/>時，而受禍一處。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0785a0907" rend="inline">豪族七萬餘生，復<note n="0785005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">見＋（見）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0785005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">見【大】，見見【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0785005"><lem wit="【大】">見</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">見見</rdg></app>生獲，
<lb n="0785a10" ed="T"/>鐵<note n="0785006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鎖＝銷【宮】</note><note n="0785006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">鎖【大】，銷【宮】</note><app n="0785006"><lem wit="【大】">鎖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">銷</rdg></app>其頸。貴姓女千人，以<note n="0785007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鎖＝槊【三】，鏟【宮】</note><note n="0785007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">鎖【大】，槊【宋】【元】【明】，鏟【宮】</note><app n="0785007"><lem wit="【大】">鎖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">槊</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">鏟</rdg></app>貫之，羅竪
<lb n="0785a11" ed="T"/>道側。貴姓年少嬰兒，置于格上，而射殺之。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0785a1117" rend="inline">時
<lb n="0785a12" ed="T"/>琉璃王，見釋摩男與眾辛苦，顧謂臣曰：「是
<lb n="0785a13" ed="T"/>何人乎？」答曰：「釋摩男。釋摩男<note n="0785008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔之〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0785008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">之【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0785008"><lem wit="【大】">之</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>來，欲有所
<lb n="0785a14" ed="T"/>乞。」王曰：「現之。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0785a1406" rend="inline">釋自陳曰：「王之大王！存遇隆
<lb n="0785a15" ed="T"/>厚，聽納所啟，當具以聞。」王識委曲，恣其所說。
<lb n="0785a16" ed="T"/>「願節威怒，<app type="star" corresp="#0783036"><lem wit="【大】">唯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">惟</rdg></app>權止兵，無令放逸，多所殘
<lb n="0785a17" ed="T"/>害。我入池中，斯須當還，與王密<note n="0785a1701" resp="CBETA" type="add">議【CB】【麗-CB】，義【大】</note><app n="0785a1701"><lem resp="CBETA.maha CBETA.say" wit="【CB】【麗-CB】">議<note type="cf1">K19n0787_p0893b09</note></lem><rdg wit="【大】">義</rdg></app>立見策也，
<lb n="0785a18" ed="T"/>待我出水，乃復燿旅。」王心與口<note n="0785009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">言＝意【宋】【宮】</note><note n="0785009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">言【大】，意【宋】【宮】</note><app n="0785009"><lem wit="【大】">言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">意</rdg></app>：「人在水
<lb n="0785a19" ed="T"/>中，勢不得久。」即聽所白。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0785a1910" rend="inline">於是摩男，為國人
<lb n="0785a20" ed="T"/>民遭大厄故，辭行入池，解髮繫樹，自沈于
<lb n="0785a21" ed="T"/>水，良久不還。王大怪焉，遂遣左右，往求<note n="0785010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">料＝撩【三】【宮】</note><note n="0785010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">料【大】，撩【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0785010"><lem wit="【大】">料</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">撩</rdg></app>
<lb n="0785a22" ed="T"/>索，於樹根下，得其尸喪，出殯池側。王甚憐
<lb n="0785a23" ed="T"/>之，有慈哀心：「用門族故，自沈而死，其義若
<lb n="0785a24" ed="T"/>茲。吾為國主，不忍小忿，豈當急戰，使所害彌
<lb n="0785a25" ed="T"/>熾乎？」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0785a2503" rend="inline">前三億人畢對<app type="star" corresp="#0784029"><lem wit="【大】">併</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">并</rdg></app>命；次三億人蒙自
<lb n="0785a26" ed="T"/>次之，救得皆視<note n="0785011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">息＝自【宮】</note><note n="0785011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">息【大】，自【宮】</note><app n="0785011"><lem wit="【大】">息</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">自</rdg></app>，奔突走脫，得全濟命；又
<lb n="0785a27" ed="T"/>三億人，修家供養，歡宴熙怡，伎樂自娛，不
<lb n="0785a28" ed="T"/>知外有<app type="star" corresp="#0784029"><lem wit="【大】">併</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">并</rdg></app>命之厄，亦不聞有奔波之怖，安
<lb n="0785a29" ed="T"/>雅如常，一無所豫。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0785a2908" rend="inline">琉璃王厚葬摩男，存寵
<pb n="0785b" ed="T" xml:id="T14.0513.0785b"/>
<lb n="0785b01" ed="T"/>其後，王平舍夷更立長，安慰畢訖，還舍衛
<lb n="0785b02" ed="T"/>國。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0785b0202" rend="inline">佛與弟子至迦維羅衛，見諸人民傷殘
<lb n="0785b03" ed="T"/>者多，又察眾女人，杌無手足耳鼻<note n="0785012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">支＝肢【三】【宮】</note><note n="0785012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">支【大】，肢【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0785012"><lem wit="【大】">支</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">肢</rdg></app>體，身
<lb n="0785b04" ed="T"/>形裸露，委<anchor xml:id="fxT14p0785b01"/>在坑塹，無用自蔽，世間苦痛如
<lb n="0785b05" ed="T"/>是，不仁之人，相害甚酷。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0785b0510" rend="inline">佛言諸比丘：「彼琉
<lb n="0785b06" ed="T"/>璃王，肆意惡逆，罪盛乃爾，却<app type="star" corresp="#0784014"><lem wit="【大】">數</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">後</rdg></app>七日，有
<lb n="0785b07" ed="T"/>地獄火，當燒殺之，現世作罪，便現世受。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0785b0716" rend="inline"><note n="0785013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">大＝太【三】【宮】</note><note n="0785013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">大【大】，太【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0785013"><lem wit="【大】">大</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">太</rdg></app>
<lb n="0785b08" ed="T"/>史奏讖，怪與佛同，王大恐怖，乘<note n="0785014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">船＝舡【宋】【宮】</note><note n="0785014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">船【大】，舡【宋】【宮】</note><app n="0785014"><lem wit="【大】">船</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">舡</rdg></app>入海，冀
<lb n="0785b09" ed="T"/>得自免，停住海中。至于七日期盡，水中則
<lb n="0785b10" ed="T"/>有自然火出，燒船及王，一時灰滅。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0785b1014" rend="inline">世尊哀
<lb n="0785b11" ed="T"/>愍諸裸露者，即以威神動忉利天紫紺之殿，
<lb n="0785b12" ed="T"/>帝釋及后、首<note n="0785015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">耶＝邪【宋】【宮】</note><note n="0785015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">耶【大】，邪【宋】【宮】</note><app n="0785015"><lem wit="【大】">耶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">邪</rdg></app>之等，無數天子各齎天衣，
<lb n="0785b13" ed="T"/>俱<note n="0785016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">供＝共【三】【宮】</note><note n="0785016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">供【大】，共【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0785016"><lem wit="【大】">供</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">共</rdg></app>來下，以服覆遍裸露厄者。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0785b1313" rend="inline">佛為眾女
<lb n="0785b14" ed="T"/>而說偈曰：</p>
<lb n="0785b15" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT14p0785b1501" rend="margin-left:1em;text-indent:-1em"><l>「諸仁目所見，</l><l>現在變如是，</l>
<lb n="0785b16" ed="T"/><l>畢故莫造新，</l><l>後可長度脫。」</l></lg>
<lb n="0785b17" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT14p0785b1701">佛歎偈已，復為說法。諸來觀者，天、龍、鬼神、
<lb n="0785b18" ed="T"/>阿須倫、迦留羅、真陀羅、摩休勒、梵志、居士、長
<lb n="0785b19" ed="T"/>者、人民，無央數千聞佛所說，五百比丘漏
<lb n="0785b20" ed="T"/>盡意解；五百梵志、其餘現人，見國荒毀傷
<lb n="0785b21" ed="T"/>殘之痛，出家遵道，皆為沙門；五百天子，立
<lb n="0785b22" ed="T"/>不起法忍；二百阿須倫、千龍王，皆發無上正
<lb n="0785b23" ed="T"/>真道意；溝<note n="0785017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">坑＝机【宋】</note><note n="0785017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">坑【大】，机【宋】</note><app n="0785017"><lem wit="【大】">坑</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">机</rdg></app>五杌裸形男女，命盡得上生
<lb n="0785b24" ed="T"/>忉利天；千五百人得見道迹；千人得不還證。</p>
<lb n="0785b25" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT14p0785b2501">佛說此已，一切遍聞，稽首而退。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0785b26" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="close"><cb:jhead><anchor xml:id="fxT14p0785b03"/>佛說琉璃王經</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
</body></text></TEI>